\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

 by 1 vector of mean 0 residuals from some conditional mean model and 
\family typewriter
p
\family default
, 
\family typewriter
o
\family default
 and 
\family typewriter
q
\family default
 are the (scalar integer) orders for the symmetric, asymmetric and lagged
 variance terms respectively.
 This function only estimated 
\shape italic
regular
\shape default
